::Prowl::

Prowl smiles at Iron Raptor, the two lovers walking into the Cybertronian 
Fire. His arm around her waist presses her to him as they walk, Prowl 
inhaling the scent of her.

"The CR chambers are this way, love," he says softly to her, steering her in 
the right difection. His imagination was already giving him immages of them 
sharing his quarters, but her needs came before his, and right now she needed 
to be repaired.
